<section class="story">
  <h2>More Than a Necklace —<br>A Piece of <em>Them</em> You Can Touch.</h2>
  <p>Photos are beautiful. Memories are precious. But nothing compares to holding a <strong>physical piece</strong> of someone you love close to your heart every single day.</p>
  <p>This vintage-inspired cylinder pendant is handcrafted in stainless steel, adorned with a genuine birthstone of your choice, and designed to hold a small portion of ashes securely inside. Screw-top design means it stays sealed — through rain, through tears, through life.</p>
</section>
